modName: Sylvanas Windrunner Queen of the Forsaken - UNPB-BBP-TBBP Conversion
summary: This mod adds Sylvanas Windrunner's armor from World of warcraft into the world of Skyrim. Note: Not my mod, a conversion, and the original mod maker is AthenaX.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds Sylvanas Windrunner's armor from World of warcraft into Skyrim. It's a female only armor, and now in glorious UNPB with an option to be BBP, or TBBP!
Note: I'm not a mod maker, don't ask me to do anything, I'm just simply uploading this. xD Also, I'm not entirely sure if the cloak works with beast races, try it out and let me or gutris1 know. No Pics ATM, but I'll make some soon.
Requirements:
UNP Blessed Body - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/? (Of course. xD)
HDT Physics Extension (If you plan to use either BBP or TBBP)- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?
XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000/?
Installation:
Drop everything (except the readme file) into your skyrim data folder, then flip it on in NMM, or use NMM to automatically do it.
Uninstallation:
Do above in reverse, or tell NMM to do it.
Permissions:
While this mod isn't exactly mine and I didn't make it, just to be safe, don't drop any of this mod on any other website but here.
I'm not a mod maker as I said, so I -can't- do any conversions. You can do that yourself, or ask someone else to, and when you do, let AthenaX know of it.
Oh, and yes, it has a working weight slider. xD
Credits:
